    Provisional TM implementation for interpreted generators, with module activators (GeneratorRuntime instances) available regardless of generate templates flag. Intended to be subclassed by activators of template/generator modules with 'generate template' flag off.

    Subclasses shall implement TemplateModuleBase.getPriorities(), fillTemplateModels(TemplateModels), TemplateModuleBase.fillReferencedGenerators(ReferencedGenerators) and TemplateModule.getTargetLanguages(). Besides, getModuleReference() and getAlias() may get overridden, to make this RT class as close as possible to future RT classes ( similar to that of fully-generated modules)
